rows.label: tlk70000070_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Me and my son scrape out an
existence here, but at least we're doing
something to keep ourselves busy.

rows.label: tlk70000070_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Oh, by the by, is it true that Feltley
Village was destroyed by this Grail
character?

rows.label: tlk70000070_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Things were already bad enough here.
Without any trade with Feltley, I'm not
sure how we'll manage...

rows.label: tlk70000070_02_msg0004
rows.name:
The king seems to be pretty well-liked,
but we don't see much of his influence
out here in the sticks.

rows.label: tlk70000070_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Maybe if we got a new king things'd
be different, but who can really say
for sure...
